  "detailed_description": "20 popular Klondike games in one.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDo you love Klondike (also known as \"Classic Solitaire\" or \"Patience\"), but want a bigger challenge?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNow you can play Klondike and other popular variants with different levels of difficulty.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe collection contains:<br />\r\n• Agnes Bernauer<br />\r\n• Batsford<br />\r\n• Blind Alleys<br />\r\n• Giant<br />\r\n• King Albert<br />\r\n• Klondike<br />\r\n• New York<br />\r\n• Pas Seul<br />\r\n• Thumb and Pouch<br />\r\n• Westcliff<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlus 10 more...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n• Unlimited undo<br />\r\n• Auto complete<br />\r\n• Statistics<br />\r\n• Rules for each game",
